Title: Mystery Meatloaf
Description:
We've been gettin' complaints right and left that the Boss-Lady gets all the good grub and leaves the scraps for the others.

Between you and I, they may be onto somethin' here. I don't even get to eat as good as she does!

We need somethin' Sezik can make a lot of that at least attempts to disguise how inedible the food is here...

I got it! Mystery Meatloaf!
ObjectivesText: Obtain 7 Chunks of Mystery Meat from the local wildlife.
